Tinley_Park.Frankfort Township, Will County, Illinoi:
Frankfort Township is located in Will County, Illinois. As of the 2010 census, its population was 57,055 and it contained 19,720 housing units.


== Geography ==
According to the 2010 census, the township has a total area of 36.83 square miles (95.4 km2), of which 36.8 square miles (95 km2) (or 99.92%) is land and 0.03 square miles (0.078 km2) (or 0.08%) is water.
